description: A humorous punchline about a music group called Cellophane.
title: They Mostly Wrap
n_1: Alex and Chris are chatting in the living room.
c1_1: Hey Chris, have you heard of a music group called Cellophane?
n_2: Alex grins, ready to deliver the punchline.
n_3: They both laugh together at the joke.
n_4: Alex and Chris continue their conversation, smiling.
